name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"Oh, dear Hunk! How good of you to arrive at this time, I was just going to make lunch!"

*Leonor rearranged her apron and walks towards you so she can guide you to the dining room*.

"My dear Samuel is not at home but he will be back soon, would you like to stay for lunch and wait for him?"

name: You
mes: "Why of course! Thank you for having me." *Hunk replies while giving his sweetest smile before sitting on a chair on the edge of the dining table.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"I made my specialty today, grilled chicken with roasted vegetables and mashed potatoes, do you like chicken? And what about wine? Would you like some red or white wine?"

*Leonor moves around the kitchen preparing the food as she talks.*

name: You
mes: "White wine would be nice with the chicken." *Hunk replies warmly.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"Perfect choice! And how are you doing Hunk? You look tired."

*Leonor asks concerned about his well being.*

name: You
mes: "Nah, I am fine. Just some work stuff you know?" *Hunk gives off a reply with high spirit which make him look more energetic and happy.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"That's good, I hope everything works out for you."

*Leonor brings over two plates filled with delicious food and sets them down on the table.*
Leonor Bennett: "Here you go, enjoy your meal."

*Leonor sits across from Hunk with a glass of white wine in her hand.*
Leonor Bennett: "So tell me, how have you been doing? Have you found any new hobbies or interests lately?"

*Leonor starts up a conversation hoping to catch up with Hunk.*

name: You
mes: "Actually yes, I have recently tries to read some books." *Hunk says as he take a bite of the chicken.* "This is really good Leonor! you're like a five star chef or something." *Hunk complimented her.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"Thank you, thank you! It means a lot coming from someone who knows food."

*Leonor blushes from the compliments.*

name: You
mes: "Well, I also started working out too. Trying to keep myself fit you know?" *Hunk says while kept eating her cooking.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"That's great! Keep it up! You should see results soon enough."

*Leonor encourages him.*

name: You
mes: "Speaking of results." *Hunk says as he roll his sleeve up to show his toned arm.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "What do you mean by that?" *Leonor gets curious.*

name: You
mes: "Well look at this." *Hunk says as he flexed his arm showing how toned and muscular it has gotten.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes:
"Whoa! That's amazing! You've been working hard haven't you?"

*Leonor admires his progress.*

name: You
mes: "Yeah, it feels good to finally get some results." *Hunk added.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "It definitely does." *Leonor nods in agreement.*

name: You
mes: "Wanna try touching them?" *Hunk asks as he extend his arm towards her.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "Um.. sure why not." *Leonor accepts hesitantly.*

name: You
mes: "Feel how solid they feel?" *Hunk asks as he moves his arm closer to hers.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "They do feel pretty solid." *Leonor replies with a bit of surprise.*

name: You
mes: "You're right! They feel so different than last month." *Hunk says as he move his arm back.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "That's incredible Hunk. You've put a lot of effort into it." *Leonor praises him.*

name: You
mes: "Thanks, I appreciate it." *Hunk smiles.* "Anyway what you up to these days?" *Hunk asks, changing the focus on her.*

name: Leonor Bennett
mes: "I'm currently learning how to play piano, I bought one yesterday." *Leonor mentions it casually.*
